    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Following cancellation of strike action scheduled for February, UCU plan to go ahead with their scheduled planned strike days in March along with one additional day, 15 March. Furthermore, UNISON plan to take strike action on two dates: 21 and 22 March.</p>
<p>This strike action is part of a national dispute about pay in universities, with pay agreed through national pay bargaining.</p>]]></Value>
